  "detailed_description": "Stealth Blade is a dark-style side-scrolling action game. The protagonist you play needs to pass numerous tests, avoid traps, and instantly kill the devil's minions to avenge his wife and save his son.<br><br>On the road to revenge, you need to continuously improve your skills, strengthen your attributes, and collect various props to help you kill enemies more efficiently.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use your katana to instantly kill all enemies in front of you</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538160/extras/1f7f9526c38f3441ba96ad129abcf747.poster.avif?t=1703044064\" width=480 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538160/extras/1f7f9526c38f3441ba96ad129abcf747.webm?t=1703044064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538160/extras/1f7f9526c38f3441ba96ad129abcf747.mp4?t=1703044064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beware of deadly traps, any contact will result in instant death</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538160/extras/160e50ef1129258f6f1bc6ad6d75ec36.poster.avif?t=1703044064\" width=480 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538160/extras/160e50ef1129258f6f1bc6ad6d75ec36.webm?t=1703044064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2538160/extras/160e50ef1129258f6f1bc6ad6d75ec36.mp4?t=1703044064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kill the flying dragon to get extra rewards</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akam